{"tid":1760712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《香港論》","createTime":"2019-11-28T11:56:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T12:29:37.000Z","uid":276188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7374afb983f8bc9e29e4addfb2edecb29d66ca1b","tid":1760712,"uid":276188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T11:56:12.000Z","msg":"香港破滅，非兵不利，戰不善，弊在懼警。懼警而力虧，破滅之道也。或曰：「和勇互喪，率懼警耶？」曰：「不懼者以懼者喪，蓋失強援，不能獨完，故曰弊在懼警也。」<br />\n<br />\n警以攻捕之外，小則獲和，大則得勇，較警之所捕，與戰勝而捕者，其實百倍；和勇之所亡，與戰敗而亡者，其實亦百倍。則警之所大欲，和勇之所大患，固不在戰矣。"},{"pid":"0f13ee68bb5febeab107e07bbd45866f242ef668","tid":1760712,"uid":276188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T11:58:44.000Z","msg":"逃跑拉嘅人數係多過攻擊拉嘅人數"},{"pid":"4c948b232f8684a7a7696a1dc751e5b3a7c554e1","tid":1760712,"uid":276188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:01:20.000Z","msg":"逃跑係冇威脅又高風險嘅選擇"},{"pid":"94715de279f8f52251df6fc276b402767a29f0da","tid":1760712,"uid":276188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:04:51.000Z","msg":"逃跑容易被逐個攻破,有攻擊氣勢就會團結一致"},{"pid":"b0962c2695f4cbe5dc008b789d1b5526dc1db2d3","tid":1760712,"uid":276188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:05:35.000Z","msg":"逃跑恐懼嘅氣氛係會傳染"},{"pid":"eafccb63f6beb99e27c874cd8ecd0988589adbe7","tid":1760712,"uid":276188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:06:11.000Z","msg":"勇氣都係會傳染"},{"pid":"0156626712973fa09063d0fc32c474d3cfd33a3f","tid":1760712,"uid":276188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:08:13.000Z","msg":"區選大勝唔係End Game"},{"pid":"d39a589294a7f78b3f722872d6f8d43834b08f32","tid":1760712,"uid":276188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:10:18.000Z","msg":"區選大勝都未改變到任何野"},{"pid":"81356915273ac3093b0aa33fbba620a630162019","tid":1760712,"uid":276188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:29:37.000Z","msg":"推"}]}